    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>During Combat </b>The duelist drinks her <i>potion of haste</i>. She attempts to disarm opponents, then makes sneak attacks even if she must feint to do so."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Anyone who questions the martial prowess of halflings should keep quiet around feisty hotspurs, as these diminutive bravos excel at poking holes in large people who underestimate them."
        }
